38
00:01:59,480 --> 00:01:59,840
Father,

39
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:00,640
That's all.

40
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:01,879
You may go now.

41
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:15,400
Mr. Liang

42
