A young lady just left you a message.

43
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,080
She said you don't need to wait for her.

44
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:19,479
She has some things to take care of.

45
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,199
Once she's finished handling things in the next few days,

46
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,280
she'll give you a call.

47
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,439
