54
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,000
Let's meet another day.

55
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,240
Alright, alright, alright.

56
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:54,759
Okay.

57
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:07,599
We fellow townsmen should help each other when we're away from home.

58
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:08,439
Right?

59
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,360
Pleasure working with you.

60
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:38,240
Stop!

61
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:40,319
Stop!

62
