Stop running!

64
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:50,759
Stop!

65
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,039
Go ahead, run!

66
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,680
Let's see where you can run to.

67
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,439
If you chase me, how can I not run?

68
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:05,879
Who are you?

69
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,159
Do I know you?

70
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:08,080
Watch.

71
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:08,840
