73
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,879
Do you know Xu Jianfeng?

74
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:17,720
He's inside.

75
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,199
Don't say I brought you here.

76
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:26,160
Draw from the wall.

77
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:27,839
Play, play, play.

78
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,040
Again.

79
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,000
How much are you betting?

80
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,439
I don't believe it.

81
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:32,720
Sixty thousand.

82
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,160
I win.

83
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:36,480
I win too.

84
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,079
Double win.

85
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:41,879
One discard, three wins.

86
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,759
My specialty.

87
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:47,920
No.

88
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:51,319
Boss Xu, your luck is pretty good.

89
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:57,680
Give me back my money.

90
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,199
Who are you?

91
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,079
I don't know you.

92
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:05,959
Eight circles.

93
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,639
Pung.

94
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,240
Five bamboos.

95
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:17,680
Tch.

96
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:18,519
What are you clicking your tongue for?

97
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,079
Can you stop being so sarcastic?

98
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:20,720
Get lost.

99
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,800
Then give me back my money.

100
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:24,560
If you don't pay me back, I'll stay here.

101
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,519
Let's see who can stand it.

102
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,519
I don't have any money.

103
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:29,639
I've got plenty of time anyway.

104
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:31,040
With your card skills,

105
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,560
even if you cheat and win more money,

106
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,279
you'll lose it all.

107
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,079
There's not a single five-ten-thousand tile on this table.

108
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,120
Why are you in such a hurry?

109
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:43,519
Play the two-ten-thousand tile.

110
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:48,000
Both players next to you want ten-thousand tiles.

111
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,199
